{
  "stem": "10587.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And every Saturday morning, we would eat in bed with-- so we would have the cakes, variety of cakes, and we used to gorge ourselves on it with milk.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I used to, with my father, to-- to the temple.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We had a beautiful temple in-- in the city of Oswiecim, which the Germans destroyed, I think.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It must have been in 1940 or maybe beginning of '41, because when I became bar mitzvah, I remember the temple was no longer there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They burned it one day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my bar mitzvah took place in-- in a basement, when people were standing guard to make sure that the Germans would not find us, because it was against the law to congregate, or to have a group of people together.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I remember that I worked very hard to do a good job, but it-- it was-- it was in a-- in-- in the basement of the-- of my grandfather's house.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The-- we-- most of the family lived in my grandfather's building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Each child used to have their own apartment, and own their own apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a-- a large complex of buildings like a square itself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was a-- it was on the main square of the town, but inside the complex there was a little square.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That-- because the building was like a-- a quadrangle building with apartments on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Two-story building.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- and stores on the first floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we used to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It wasn't too far from the temple, so we used to walk every Friday night, Saturday morning, and during high holidays or-- to the temple.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My grandfather used to wear a top hat.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
